snippet.title: PAC-MAN Championship Edition 2 - Announcement Trailer | PS4, XB1, PC
snippet.description:
THE PAC-MAN CHAMPIONSHIP SERIES RETURNS WITH ALL-NEW SURPRISES!

Featuring eye-popping 3D graphics and funky visuals, the latest version of the classic game takes chomping and chasing through mazes to a whole new level! 

PAC-MAN CE2 is out September 2016
